p.k: The Wattersons transform their house into The Big House. / The Wattersons discover a family of cartoon copycats who mimic their every move. / Grandpa Louie has a new online friend - the only problem is she isn’t real. / The kids find out that Richard has been being picked on by the same person since high school. / Gumball must learn to say “no” when Carrie the Ghost uses his body against his will.
